com.wedriveu.mobile.login.router

Interface LoginRouter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DialogProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MainActivity

    public interface LoginRouter
extends DialogProvider
    LoginRouter is the interface used by the LoginViewModel logic to switch to the next Fragment transaction. Eg. After the user clicks on Login button, the login process is terminated and the App performs a fragment transaction to the Scheduling application component.
